column2: "Well, looks like he's not here, let's keep moving."
"It feels like you haven't seen Camalots in a long time, is he okay?"
"Hm? Meaning, \"hasn't he kicked the bucket yet\"?"
"You don't need to think about my feelings, everything dies one way or another."
"All I can do is hope that he's doing okay until I can confirm one way or the other."
"That goes for him as well, all he can do is hope that I'm waiting for him."
"In this situation that's really all there is to it, no?"
"You're right! Alright, let's really do our best to look!"
"No, uh... I think we'd be better off if you didn't try hard like that."
